==English==
===Noun===
'''mackinaw skiff'''
# A cargo boat, with a large flat bottom and sharp ends, formerly used on the Great Lakes and the Missouri River (to a lesser extent, elsewhere).
# A shooner-rigged boat once used on the Great Lakes.

